text: NTN may refer to: *NTN Buzztime, an entertainment company *NTN (TV channel) (), television channel in Ukraine *Nike Team Nationals, a cross-country meet *New Telemark Norm, a ski binding system *NTN Corporation, bearing manufacturer *National Terminal Number ==Science== *Netrins or NTN1, class of proteins *Neurturin, glial protein *Neurotactin, protein now known as CX3CL1
